 />\n不要挑機<br />\n只要反黑 集中政權 政X警X黑<br />\n叫多幾個FD一齊出發，示威行完一齊走<br />\n唔好留到入夜，達到目的就要走，千祺唔好留守"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:21:53.000Z","msg":"我地要諗點connect 最多人"},{"pid":"9979ce1b1b35462b50e196c1cfc29dd643f12c17","tid":1357430,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:35:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e42ab05c38c114a3e5cf12a1d98f1debef2ef998","tid":1357430,"uid":219244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"中環遇遊行堵路 貨Van司機遭圍毆扑車「你哋示威 留番條生路畀我」<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190723%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=80b4dd24\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我知貨van司機比人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打爛架車</strong></span>係啲長期輩gp瘋傳<br />\n我有睇過幾段片<br />\n都有睇過連登post<br />\n<br />\n件事大概係有人係入隧道前提過佢前面有路障佢都照入隧道<br />\n結果係隧道另一面遇見路障<br />\n想衝前突破路障時被阻止<br />\n跟住落車同義士口角<br />\n仲自己郁手清走路障<br />\n過程中有一個義士攞住雪糕筒琴住佢個車cam<br />\n結果佢郁手推開嗰個義士<br />\n跟住佢就俾人圍毆同砸車了<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢件事大家太衝動<br />\n果條友又以為義士搞佢架車所以郁手推開佢<br />\n條友係串串貢就移開路障，但大家可唔可以冷靜啲<br />\n打佢都算啦，鬼叫佢郁手推人先<br />\n但砸車對成件事有乜幫助？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成件事比港台直播晒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗令個司機好心痛同送彈藥藍絲外，仲有乜用？<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190721/_2019072120020210202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190721%2F_2019072120020210202.jpg&h=f55f2f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721我一開始見到黑警話示威者打車我都好詫異<br />\n但check返原來係呢單野<br />\n<br />\n放火都話係燒垃圾丶做路障阻止黑警包抄，<strong>無任何市民有損失</strong><br />\n但打車真係過左<br />\n<br />\n唔係指責，件事已經做咗<br />\n但希望以後大家都保持冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">諗清楚自己每個action對成個活動有乜幫助</span></strong></span><br />\n記清楚我地<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標係五大訴求</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>所有武力對凖政權，而唔係人民鬥人民</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f213d67cd8740cd807ac03990543464b67ef755a","tid":1357430,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e42ab05c38c114a3e5cf12a1d98f1debef2ef998","tid":1357430,"uid":219244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"中環遇遊行堵路 貨Van司機遭圍毆扑車「你哋示威 留番條生路畀我」<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190723%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=80b4dd24\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我知貨van司機比人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打爛架車</strong></span>係啲長期輩gp瘋傳<br />\n我有睇過幾段片<br />\n都有睇過連登post<br />\n<br />\n件事大概係有人係入隧道前提過佢前面有路障佢都照入隧道<br />\n結果係隧道另一面遇見路障<br />\n想衝前突破路障時被阻止<br />\n跟住落車同義士口角<br />\n仲自己郁手清走路障<br />\n過程中有一個義士攞住雪糕筒琴住佢個車cam<br />\n結果佢郁手推開嗰個義士<br />\n跟住佢就俾人圍毆同砸車了<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢件事大家太衝動<br />\n果條友又以為義士搞佢架車所以郁手推開佢<br />\n條友係串串貢就移開路障，但大家可唔可以冷靜啲<br />\n打佢都算啦，鬼叫佢郁手推人先<br />\n但砸車對成件事有乜幫助？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成件事比港台直播晒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗令個司機好心痛同送彈藥藍絲外，仲有乜用？<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190721/_2019072120020210202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190721%2F_2019072120020210202.jpg&h=f55f2f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721我一開始見到黑警話示威者打車我都好詫異<br />\n但check返原來係呢單野<br />\n<br />\n放火都話係燒垃圾丶做路障阻止黑警包抄，<strong>無任何市民有損失</strong><br />\n但打車真係過左<br />\n<br />\n唔係指責，件事已經做咗<br />\n但希望以後大家都保持冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">諗清楚自己每個action對成個活動有乜幫助</span></strong></span><br />\n記清楚我地<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標係五大訴求</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>所有武力對凖政權，而唔係人民鬥人民</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"好多人話佢開車撞人，<br />\n其實有冇片證明到佢開車撞人？"},{"pid":"8a4881dd8d340ed72e0b3a7de761cee7be8b51c7","tid":1357430,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:50:44.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"12fdebae2dfde69612ecea2d920b3e42ff1bc3ed","tid":1357430,"uid":219244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f213d67cd8740cd807ac03990543464b67ef755a","tid":1357430,"uid":230146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e42ab05c38c114a3e5cf12a1d98f1debef2ef998","tid":1357430,"uid":219244,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"中環遇遊行堵路 貨Van司機遭圍毆扑車「你哋示威 留番條生路畀我」<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190723%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU3XW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=80b4dd24\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20190723/mobile/odn-20190723-0723_00176_019.html</a><br />\n<br />\n我知貨van司機比人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打爛架車</strong></span>係啲長期輩gp瘋傳<br />\n我有睇過幾段片<br />\n都有睇過連登post<br />\n<br />\n件事大概係有人係入隧道前提過佢前面有路障佢都照入隧道<br />\n結果係隧道另一面遇見路障<br />\n想衝前突破路障時被阻止<br />\n跟住落車同義士口角<br />\n仲自己郁手清走路障<br />\n過程中有一個義士攞住雪糕筒琴住佢個車cam<br />\n結果佢郁手推開嗰個義士<br />\n跟住佢就俾人圍毆同砸車了<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢件事大家太衝動<br />\n果條友又以為義士搞佢架車所以郁手推開佢<br />\n條友係串串貢就移開路障，但大家可唔可以冷靜啲<br />\n打佢都算啦，鬼叫佢郁手推人先<br />\n但砸車對成件事有乜幫助？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>成件事比港台直播晒</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除咗令個司機好心痛同送彈藥藍絲外，仲有乜用？<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190721/_2019072120020210202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190721%2F_2019072120020210202.jpg&h=f55f2f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721我一開始見到黑警話示威者打車我都好詫異<br />\n但check返原來係呢單野<br />\n<br />\n放火都話係燒垃圾丶做路障阻止黑警包抄，<strong>無任何市民有損失</strong><br />\n但打車真係過左<br />\n<br />\n唔係指責，件事已經做咗<br />\n但希望以後大家都保持冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">諗清楚自己每個action對成個活動有乜幫助</span></strong></span><br />\n記清楚我地<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目標係五大訴求</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>所有武力對凖政權，而唔係人民鬥人民</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"好多人話佢開車撞人，<br />\n其實有冇片證明到佢開車撞人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:00:39.000Z","msg":"有一段片係架車向前<br />\n跟住有個人阻止<br />\n跟住佢就落車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n段片有義士樣就唔share了<br />\n但睇情況佢應該唔係想撞人(車前面冇人) 似想衝路障多啲<br />\n<br />\n總之大家冷靜啲啦<br />\n打佢就算，砸車真係免得過就唔好做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ca1a360d979c5bae0d57e1093b100df45dec01","tid":1357430,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"544b9de67fa1905da95548d654b77b78d12e6432","tid":1357430,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,